This dataset represents e-commerce sales transactions, including customer behavior, product details, and regional performance. It is designed to analyze sales trends, payment preferences, and business profitability.

 Such datasets typically include transaction-level data like orders, regions, and payment methods, enabling analysis of trends and customer behavior

  Key Columns Used
Order ID → Unique identifier for each transaction
Date → Transaction date
Customer Name → Name of the customer
Country → Name of the country
Region → Sales region (e.g., Europe, North America)
Product Category → Type of product sold
Product Name → Name of the product
Quantity → Number of units sold
Unit Price → Price per item
Total Revenue → Total sales value
Shipping Cost → Tells shipping cost per item
Payment Method → Credit Card, PayPal, COD, Bank Transfer
Discount Applied → Whether discount was given
Profit / Profit Margin → Business profitability
Weighted margin → Tells overall profitability
Sales Remark → Tells sales feedback
Profit Remarks → Tells profit feedback
Years → Transaction month
Month → Transaction Year

These types of columns are standard in e-commerce datasets used to analyze trends, customer behavior, and sales performance

What This Data Helps Analyze:
Regional sales performance
Customer payment preferences
Impact of discounts on sales
Profitability across segments
Seasonal trends in revenue

Key Findings
Europe generated the highest sales.
North America had the highest weighted profit margin.
Consumer segment performed best.
High discounts reduced profitability.
Most commonly used payment method is credit card
Performance need to improve for low margin categories like office supplies
Business has consistent sales around the years with slight improvement in marketing strategies need to increase in before fall season

Business Recommendations

Focus expansion in Europe (sales growth) ​

Strengthen North America (profitability) ​

Target Consumer segment for marketing ​

Improve low-margin categories ​

Focus on using Credit card payment method on most of the regions​

Align strategies with seasonal demand ​

Avoid high discount on products to protect the profitability and improve the sales ​
